article.description: — Michael Flowers posted 18 points and seven rebounds as South Alabama edged past Troy 73-70 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Flowers scores 18 to carry South Alabama over Troy 73-70
article.linkText: Flowers scores 18 to carry South Alabama over Troy 73-70
article.story: MOBILE, Ala. -- — Michael Flowers posted 18 points and seven rebounds as South Alabama edged past Troy 73-70 on Thursday night. Tyreke Locure had 14 points, seven rebounds and seven assists for South Alabama (13-8, 7-5 Sun Belt Conference), which earned its fifth straight victory. John Pettway added 14 points. Kayo Goncalves had 11 points and seven rebounds. Sam Iorio tied a career high with six blocks plus eight points. Nick Stampley had 20 points and seven rebounds for the Trojans (10-11, 4-7). Duke Miles added 14 points and six assists. Khalyl Waters had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
